Package: atlas.plot
Type: Package
Title: Automated Plotting in R
Version: 1.0.3
Author: Cao Bittencourt
Maintainer: Cao Bittencourt <caobittencourt@gmail.com>
Description: This package streamlines repetitive plotting procedures. Currently, it supports only 'ggplot2' and similar packages.
